      "para_id": "Q001580.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , his master , Ninḫedu , the child of Ur-Bau , ruler of Lagaš , his spouse , dedicated this ( round slab ) for the well-being of Nammaḫni , ruler of Lagaš , and also for her own well-being ."
    }
  ],
